      "title": "How To Get A Free Laptop Or Desktop?",
      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>How To Get A Free Laptop Or Desktop?</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<p>Various charities, businesses, and government assistance programs, including those for people with EBT food stamps, offer these devices with a focus on helping students in grades K-12 or adults working from home. Click through to see which one suits you!</p>\n<img alt=\"How To Get A Free Laptop Or Desktop?_1\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-to-get-a-free-laptop-or-desktop/how-to-get-a-free-laptop-or-desktop_1.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-to-get-a-free-laptop-or-desktop/how-to-get-a-free-laptop-or-desktop_1.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-to-get-a-free-laptop-or-desktop/how-to-get-a-free-laptop-or-desktop_1.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-to-get-a-free-laptop-or-desktop/how-to-get-a-free-laptop-or-desktop_1.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n</img></div>"
