      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>How To Get A Free Laptop Or Desktop?</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<h4>2. Government Assistance Programs </h4>\n<p>Government programs like EBT and SNAP Food stamps provide free laptops or desktop computers to low-income, seniors, or disabled adults. Local schools, in partnership with organizations like United Way, also participate in giving away free laptops and tablets​​.</p>\n<img alt=\"How To Get A Free Laptop Or Desktop?_3\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-to-get-a-free-laptop-or-desktop/how-to-get-a-free-laptop-or-desktop_3.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-to-get-a-free-laptop-or-desktop/how-to-get-a-free-laptop-or-desktop_3.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-to-get-a-free-laptop-or-desktop/how-to-get-a-free-laptop-or-desktop_3.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-to-get-a-free-laptop-or-desktop/how-to-get-a-free-laptop-or-desktop_3.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n</img></div>"
